      "macro_transmission": "EUR cost of one USD from the ECB reference rate."
    },
    "missing_data_policy": "Raw missing values remain null. BLS computer CPI October 2025 is linearly interpolated only inside the derived six-month calculation and is visibly documented. Eurostat June 2026 and BLS semiconductor PPI June 2026 use the latest available May observation for the June backcast.",
    "future_model_rule": "After at least 36 monthly observations, compare these fixed thresholds with a rolling percentile model before changing the published method. Any change must be versioned."
